Privacy Policy
Data Collection: The bot collects minimal user data, limited to necessary information such as user IDs and message content for its functionality. No personal or sensitive data is collected.

Data Usage: Collected data is used solely for providing and improving bot services. Data is not shared with third parties.

Data Storage: Any data stored is kept secure and is only retained as long as necessary for the bot's operation. Regular audits are conducted to ensure data integrity and security.

Data Access: Users can request to view or delete their data by contacting the botâ€™s support team. We aim to process such requests promptly.

Third-Party Services: If the bot uses third-party services, their privacy policies apply. We ensure that these services adhere to strict privacy standards.

Updates: The privacy policy may be updated periodically. Users will be notified of significant changes.
